title: The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim VR
notes: Takes forever to start up. Significant performance hit and async reprojection is glitchy. Ran directly off a Windows NTFS partition.
Performance is surprisingly good, with no reprojection or judder. Some sounds (like dialogue) are however missing.
